OL,3,CMore cases to be investigated as part
OL,4,Cof hospital medical negligence probe
OL,6,FA police force investigating around
OL,7,F200 cases at a hospital trust over
OL,8,Fallegations of medical negligence has
OL,9,Fexpanded its probe to include a "small
OL,10,Fnumber" relating to a specialist
OL,11,Fsurgery.
OL,13,FSussex Police are investigating cases
OL,14,Fof patient deaths and serious injury
OL,15,Fat the Royal Sussex County Hospital in
OL,16,FBrighton between 2015 to 2021,
OL,17,Frelating to neurosurgery and general
OL,18,Fsurgery.
OL,26,@qD@aOUrD@GO]
