OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776352251
OL,3,CMore cases to be investigated as part
OL,4,Cof hospital medical negligence probe
OL,6,FThe cases are being reviewed by
OL,7,Fspecialist consultant surgeons
OL,8,Findependent of the trust that runs the
OL,9,Fhospital, the University Hospitals
OL,10,FSussex NHS Foundation Trust.
OL,12,FClaims of medical negligence were made
OL,13,Fby two consultant surgeons who lost
OL,14,Ftheir jobs after blowing the whistle
OL,15,Fabout patient safety, The Guardian
OL,16,Fpreviously reported.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
