PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776352251
OL,3,CMore cases to be investigated as part
OL,4,Cof hospital medical negligence probe
OL,6,FPolice began assessing allegations in
OL,7,F2023 and on Wednesday confirmed
OL,8,Fofficers are starting to review cases
OL,9,Frelating to cardiothoracic surgery,
OL,10,Fwhich involves operating on heart,
OL,11,Flungs and other chest organs.
OL,13,FA force spokeswoman said: "As a result
OL,14,Fof a further witness coming forward
OL,15,Fduring the course of the
OL,16,Finvestigation, police are now starting
OL,17,Fto review a small number of cases
OL,18,Frelating to cardiothoracic surgery at
OL,19,Fthe Royal Sussex County Hospital.
OL,26,@uD@[OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
