PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776352251
OL,3,CMore cases to be investigated as part
OL,4,Cof hospital medical negligence probe
OL,6,F"These inquiries are at an early
OL,7,Fstage, and officers are contacting
OL,8,Frelevant patients and families
OL,9,Fdirectly to provide information and
OL,10,Fsupport while this is ongoing."
OL,12,FThe force added the investigation,
OL,13,Fnamed Operation Bramber, is likely to
OL,14,Ftake "some time" to complete due to
OL,15,Fthe complex nature of the inquiries.
OL,17,FThe hospital trust is "co-operating
OL,18,Ffully" with the probe, Sussex Police
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@_O]vD@FOUvD@PO]yD@WOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
