FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776352251
OL,3,CMore cases to be investigated as part
OL,4,Cof hospital medical negligence probe
OL,6,FIt's been reported that a letter sent
OL,7,Fto some families by police, said that
OL,8,Fof cases assessed so far, the medical
OL,9,Fexpert reviews have not revealed any
OL,10,Fevidence that would support a criminal
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FProf Katie Urch, chief medical officer
OL,14,Fat University Hospitals Sussex NHS
OL,15,FTrust, said: "We continue to co-
OL,16,Foperate fully with Sussex Police, and
OL,17,Fwe will do everything we can to help
OL,18,Ftheir team to give families the
OL,19,Fclarity they need, as quickly as
OL,20,Fpossible.
OL,26,@wD@NOU
