CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776352251
OL,3,CMore cases to be investigated as part
OL,4,Cof hospital medical negligence probe
OL,6,F"Safety is always our priority, and we
OL,7,Fremain absolutely committed to acting
OL,8,Fimmediately on behalf of our patients,
OL,9,Fif the police investigation should
OL,10,Fever raise any concerns about the
OL,11,Fstandards of hospital services being
OL,12,Fdelivered now."
